    <h3>About TrendingTopics.org</h3>
    <p>
    This site was built by <a href="http://www.datawrangling.com">Data Wrangling</a> to demonstrate how Hadoop can power a simple data driven website. The trend statistics and time series data that run the site are updated periodically by launching a temporary EC2 cluster running the <a href="http://cloudera.com/">Cloudera Hadoop Distribution</a>.  Our initial seed data includes the content of wikipedia and hourly article traffic logs from the wikipedia squid proxy collected by <a href="http://dammit.lt/">Domas Mituzas</a>.  We made the first 7 months of this data available as an <a href="http://aws.amazon.com/publicdatasets/">Amazon Public Dataset</a>.
    </p>
